highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Malaysia. “Golden” is the highest at #16.
“milk of the madonna” by Deftones is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Malaysia at #65.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Malaysia the longest, at 147 days straight.
“Saya Anak Malaysia” by Dr Sam is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Malaysia, up 28 spots at #64.
